'''藍湖'''（Blue Lake）是位於[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]][[尼爾森湖國家公園|尼爾森湖國家公園]]內的一個小湖。在當地[[毛利人|毛利人]]社群中，藍湖是一個信仰對象。藍湖以其清澈的湖水而著稱，是紐西蘭透明度最高的湖泊<ref name="NIWA">{{cite web|title=Nelson’s Blue Lake – The clearest freshwater ever reported|url=http://www.niwa.co.nz/news/nelson%E2%80%99s-blue-lake-%E2%80%93-the-clearest-freshwater-ever-reported|publisher=NIWA|accessdate=2011-12-20|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209125216/https://niwa.co.nz/news/nelson%e2%80%99s-blue-lake-%e2%80%93-the-clearest-freshwater-ever-reported|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Nelson's Blue Lake clearest|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10774272|accessdate=20 December 2011|newspaper=New Zealand Herald|date=2011-12-20|archive-date=2020-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224185946/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/nz/news/article.cfm?c_id=1&objectid=10774272|dead-url=no}}</ref>。藍湖水溫較低，全年水溫約在{{convert|5|to|8|C|F}}。
